{"ja470:0.1":"Jataka ","ja470:0.2":"Dvadasakanipata ","ja470:0.3":"Culakunalavagga ","ja470:0.4":"7. Kosiyajataka ","ja470:1.1":"“Neva kinami napi vikkinami, ","ja470:1.2":"Na capi me sannicayo ca atthi; ","ja470:1.3":"Sukiccharupam vatidam parittam, ","ja470:1.4":"Patthodano nalamayam duvinnam”. ","ja470:2.1":"“Appamha appakam dajja, ","ja470:2.2":"anumajjhato majjhakam; ","ja470:2.3":"Bahumha bahukam dajja, ","ja470:2.4":"adanam nupapajjati. ","ja470:3.1":"Tam tam vadami kosiya, ","ja470:3.2":"dehi danani bhunja ca”. ","ja470:3.3":"Ariyamaggam samaruha, ","ja470:3.4":"nekasi labhate sukham. ","ja470:4.1":"“Moghancassa hutam hoti, ","ja470:4.2":"moghancapi samihitam; ","ja470:4.3":"Atithismim yo nisinnasmim, ","ja470:4.4":"eko bhunjati bhojanam. ","ja470:5.1":"Tam tam vadami kosiya, ","ja470:5.2":"dehi danani bhunja ca; ","ja470:5.3":"Ariyamaggam samaruha, ","ja470:5.4":"nekasi labhate sukham”. ","ja470:6.1":"“Saccancassa hutam hoti, ","ja470:6.2":"saccancapi samihitam; ","ja470:6.3":"Atithismim yo nisinnasmim, ","ja470:6.4":"neko bhunjati bhojanam. ","ja470:7.1":"Tam tam vadami kosiya, ","ja470:7.2":"dehi danani bhunja ca; ","ja470:7.3":"Ariyamaggam samaruha, ","ja470:7.4":"nekasi labhate sukham”. ","ja470:8.1":"“Saranca juhati poso, ","ja470:8.2":"bahukaya gayaya ca; ","ja470:8.3":"Done timbarutitthasmim, ","ja470:8.4":"sighasote mahavahe. ","ja470:9.1":"Atra cassa hutam hoti, ","ja470:9.2":"atra cassa samihitam; ","ja470:9.3":"Atithismim yo nisinnasmim, ","ja470:9.4":"neko bhunjati bhojanam. ","ja470:10.1":"Tam tam vadami kosiya, ","ja470:10.2":"dehi danani bhunja ca; ","ja470:10.3":"Ariyamaggam samaruha, ","ja470:10.4":"nekasi labhate sukham”. ","ja470:11.1":"“Balisanhi so nigilati, ","ja470:11.2":"dighasuttam sabandhanam; ","ja470:11.3":"Atithismim yo nisinnasmim, ","ja470:11.4":"eko bhunjati bhojanam. ","ja470:12.1":"Tam tam vadami kosiya, ","ja470:12.2":"dehi danani bhunja ca; ","ja470:12.3":"Ariyamaggam samaruha, ","ja470:12.4":"nekasi labhate sukham”. ","ja470:13.1":"“Ularavanna vata brahmana ime, ","ja470:13.2":"Ayanca vo sunakho kissa hetu; ","ja470:13.3":"Uccavacam vannanibham vikubbati, ","ja470:13.4":"Akkhatha no brahmana ke nu tumhe”. ","ja470:14.1":"“Cando ca suriyo ca ubho idhagata, ","ja470:14.2":"Ayam pana matali devasarathi; ","ja470:14.3":"Sakkohamasmi tidasanamindo, ","ja470:14.4":"Eso ca kho pancasikhoti vuccati”. ","ja470:15.1":"“Panissara mudinga ca, ","ja470:15.2":"murajalambarani ca; ","ja470:15.3":"Suttamenam pabodhenti, ","ja470:15.4":"patibuddho ca nandati”. ","ja470:16.1":"“Ye kecime maccharino kadariya, ","ja470:16.2":"Paribhasaka samanabrahmananam; ","ja470:16.3":"Idheva nikkhippa sariradeham, ","ja470:16.4":"Kayassa bheda nirayam vajanti”. ","ja470:17.1":"“Ye kecime suggatimasamana, ","ja470:17.2":"Dhamme thita samyame samvibhage; ","ja470:17.3":"Idheva nikkhippa sariradeham, ","ja470:17.4":"Kayassa bheda sugatim vajanti. ","ja470:18.1":"Tvam nosi nati purimasu jatisu, ","ja470:18.2":"So macchari rosako papadhammo; ","ja470:18.3":"Taveva atthaya idhagatamha, ","ja470:18.4":"Ma papadhammo nirayam gamittha”. ","ja470:19.1":"“Addha hi mam vo hitakama, ","ja470:19.2":"yam mam samanusasatha; ","ja470:19.3":"Soham tatha karissami, ","ja470:19.4":"sabbam vuttam hitesibhi. ","ja470:20.1":"Esahamajjeva uparamami, ","ja470:20.2":"Na capiham kinci kareyya papam; ","ja470:20.3":"Na capi me kinci adeyyamatthi, ","ja470:20.4":"Na capidatva udakam pivami. ","ja470:21.1":"Evanca me dadato sabbakalam, ","ja470:21.2":"Bhoga ime vasava khiyissanti; ","ja470:21.3":"Tato aham pabbajissami sakka, ","ja470:21.4":"Hitvana kamani yathodhikani”ti. ","ja470:22.1":"Kosiyajatakam sattamam. "}